# Aether Agent — .gitignore
#
# Session memory lives in root AETHER.md §18 (committed). Optional legacy
# `.agent/session-context.md` pointer stubs may be committed if your toolchain
# requires that path — do not add it here.

# OpenCode session dump files (ephemeral, not project artifacts)
session-ses_*.md

.gemini/

# Reference repositories (cloned for synthesis, not distributed)
references/

# Historical archives
archived/*
!archived/references/
archived/references/*
!archived/references/create-aether-agent/
!archived/references/create-aether-agent/**

# Private AI operating documents (kept offline to preserve IP)
docs/scan-reports/
docs/audit-reports/
docs/master-plans/
docs/research/
docs/maps/
docs/implementation_plan.md

__pycache__/

# Node modules (MCP servers)
node_modules/

# Environment files
.env
*.local

# OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini

# Editor files
*.swp
*.swo
*~
